[Fengman House]

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:32.910
Take care.

00:02:32.910 --> 00:02:33.360
Come again.

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:33.910
Visit us next time.

00:02:33.910 --> 00:02:34.430
Please come often.

00:02:34.430 --> 00:02:35.750
The Crown Prince Investiture Ceremony
and the Heaven Worship Ritual

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:37.150
will begin soon.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:39.710
We must prepare a nice surprise

00:02:39.710 --> 00:02:40.910
for the Eldest Prince.

00:02:40.910 --> 00:02:41.910
Chief Commander.

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:42.690
Don't worry.

00:02:42.910 --> 00:02:43.560
Our men

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:45.280
have already been
making their way into the city.

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:46.910
Have all the flowers arrived?

00:02:46.910 --> 00:02:49.640
Ten carts of flowers
have arrived in the capital.

00:02:49.750 --> 00:02:50.750
Chief Commander.

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:52.650
Aren't these enough

00:02:52.910 --> 00:02:55.400
to blast the entire ceremony site?

00:02:58.910 --> 00:02:59.800
Chief Commander.

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:02.150
Everything is ready.
We're just waiting for the right moment.

00:03:02.150 --> 00:03:02.800
Finally,

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:04.560
less than two weeks to go.

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:05.750
I can't wait

00:03:05.750 --> 00:03:08.030
to scout the ceremony venue.

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:09.630
Be careful.

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:12.190
I've heard that the Longxiang Guards

00:03:12.190 --> 00:03:14.250
have tightened security in the city.

00:03:14.870 --> 00:03:16.600
Don't worry, Chief Commander.

00:03:16.630 --> 00:03:18.800
I'm an expert at disguise.

00:03:18.870 --> 00:03:21.210
[Taiji Hall]

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.760
Everyone be careful.

00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:27.280
The Crown Prince Investiture Ceremony
is approaching.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.710
We can't afford any mistakes.

00:03:28.710 --> 00:03:29.240
Yes.

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:30.730
Put it here. Be careful.

00:03:31.750 --> 00:03:33.000
This fool

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.800
is now in charge of supervising
the Crown Prince Investiture Ceremony.

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:38.190
What if he has the Defense Map on him?

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:45.690
Are you okay?

00:03:47.030 --> 00:03:47.910
It's you.

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.420
What a coincidence seeing you again.

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:53.430
My Lord, your hand is bleeding.

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:55.810
It's just a small wound. It's nothing.

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.870
As a doctor,

00:03:57.870 --> 00:03:59.400
seeing someone injured and not helping

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:01.120
would bring bad karma.

00:04:06.910 --> 00:04:08.170
This wound of yours...

00:04:21.269 --> 00:04:22.670
If it hurts, just cry out.

00:04:22.870 --> 00:04:24.870
There's nobody else around anyway.

00:04:25.430 --> 00:04:26.230
Doctor, do you

00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:28.640
treat all your patients this intimately?

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:30.160
Only with you,

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.870
patients who don't
take care of themselves.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.130
I've searched everywhere.

00:04:36.270 --> 00:04:37.270
It seems today

00:04:37.270 --> 00:04:39.400
he doesn't have the Defense Map on him.

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:44.830
That's done.

00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:45.430
Remember,

00:04:45.630 --> 00:04:47.430
keep this wound dry for the next few days.

00:04:47.430 --> 00:04:48.030
Farewell.

00:04:49.830 --> 00:04:50.390
Sir!

00:04:51.070 --> 00:04:52.630
You've saved me and my family twice.

00:04:52.630 --> 00:04:54.000
May I ask your name?

00:04:56.190 --> 00:04:57.480
Just call me Li Sang.

00:04:58.360 --> 00:04:58.920
Mr. Li.

00:04:59.510 --> 00:05:00.110
Farewell.

00:05:07.750 --> 00:05:08.310
Five.

00:05:08.510 --> 00:05:09.040
Look!

00:05:09.270 --> 00:05:10.070
Sky lanterns.

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:11.800
Let's set off one too.

00:05:13.630 --> 00:05:14.760
Make a wish quickly.

00:05:17.390 --> 00:05:18.520
I pray to the heavens

00:05:19.070 --> 00:05:20.000
that in this life

00:05:20.190 --> 00:05:22.250
I may live a peaceful and simple life.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:23.830
And that Jun Che

00:05:23.830 --> 00:05:25.010
will never become a tyrant.

00:05:25.010 --> 00:05:28.400
♪ I was deeply in love ♪

00:05:30.390 --> 00:05:31.100
Why are you making wishes
with your eyes open?

00:05:31.100 --> 00:05:32.630
♪ A tumultuous tale of love and hate ♪

00:05:32.630 --> 00:05:35.290
Heaven will only help
if you're sincere enough.

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:37.100
I don't have any wishes
I can't fulfill myself

00:05:37.100 --> 00:05:37.560
♪ Who should I ask when I'm trapped? ♪

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:39.159
that require heaven's help.

00:05:39.720 --> 00:05:40.240
My Lady.

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:41.430
I advise you,

00:05:41.750 --> 00:05:43.540
instead of begging heaven and earth,
you'd better beg me.

00:05:43.540 --> 00:05:45.750
♪ Heal the scars made in my old dreams ♪

00:05:45.750 --> 00:05:48.040
Then I want it to snow right now.

00:05:48.510 --> 00:05:49.360
Snow?

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:53.760
♪ Life gives me joy and sorrow ♪

00:05:56.550 --> 00:06:00.280
♪ A kiss stirs love and hate ♪

00:06:01.260 --> 00:06:03.820
♪ Who can save me from my old dreams? ♪

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:04.920
♪ Who can save me from this lonely city? ♪

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:05.980
What are you doing?

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:07.650
Didn't you want to see snow?

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:12.600
♪ Who can give me freedom? ♪

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.400
Do you like it?

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:14.270
♪ Dare not ask a lovesick soul ♪

00:06:14.270 --> 00:06:15.930
This is the snow I made for you.

00:06:17.290 --> 00:06:19.690
♪ At midnight, moonlight shines brightly ♪

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:20.430
Five. This... This isn't snow.

00:06:20.430 --> 00:06:21.430
♪ Who is the fickle lover
I'm waiting for? ♪

00:06:21.430 --> 00:06:22.390
It's ashes.

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:23.920
Aren't ashes and snow

00:06:24.190 --> 00:06:25.120
the same thing?

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:26.490
They're both white.

00:06:26.490 --> 00:06:27.070
♪ Love disappeared while hatred lasts ♪

00:06:27.070 --> 00:06:28.600
They both fall from the sky.

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:29.820
You can't just use this kind of

00:06:29.820 --> 00:06:30.560
♪ Realize that a good start
does not guarantee a happy ending ♪

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:32.800
reckless method to make snow
without caring about others.

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:34.120
You liked it, so I made it for you.

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:34.800
♪ Forget the one who never
returned in my old dreams ♪

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:36.730
You burned all those sky lanterns.

00:06:36.830 --> 00:06:38.159
What about all those people's wishes?

00:06:38.159 --> 00:06:39.040
And those sparks

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:40.800
could set someone's house on fire.

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.930
So what if they burn?

00:06:42.159 --> 00:06:43.270
It's no big deal.

00:06:43.270 --> 00:06:45.000
How can you be so unreasonable?

00:06:45.390 --> 00:06:46.450
I'm unreasonable?

00:06:47.070 --> 00:06:48.670
Then you're just being nosy.

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:50.900
I'm not arguing with you anymore!

00:06:53.159 --> 00:06:54.890
I just wanted to make you happy.

00:06:55.630 --> 00:06:56.690
What did I do wrong?

00:06:56.690 --> 00:06:57.390
[Fengman House]

00:06:57.390 --> 00:06:59.480
Ladies, come in and rest.

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:00.070
We're closed.

00:07:00.070 --> 00:07:01.270
Alright.

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:07.240
Chief Commander.

00:07:07.310 --> 00:07:08.570
What's wrong with you?

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:09.800
Why are you so angry?

00:07:13.390 --> 00:07:14.920
Looking at you like this,

00:07:15.070 --> 00:07:17.430
don't tell me you're in love with someone.

00:07:20.220 --> 00:07:22.120
[Lu's Mansion]

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:22.720
Yingying.

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.480
I heard that on the day Ding Huairen died,

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:26.410
you happened to give Five a day off.

00:07:26.430 --> 00:07:27.760
He wasn't home that day.

00:07:28.120 --> 00:07:30.160
The Crown Prince asked me
to find out who killed Ding Huairen.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:32.000
Five is from the Yue State
and knows martial arts.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.430
According to witnesses' descriptions,

00:07:33.430 --> 00:07:36.430
his appearance matches
the suspect's quite closely.

00:07:37.870 --> 00:07:39.120
Of course not, Hui.

00:07:39.310 --> 00:07:42.070
I saw Five return early that day.

00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:43.530
It couldn't have been him.

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:46.360
Even so,

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:48.120
Five's background is suspicious.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.320
He's very dangerous.

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:51.159
He absolutely cannot stay
at the Lu's Mansion.

00:07:51.159 --> 00:07:51.750
Why not?

00:07:56.390 --> 00:07:57.630
You don't want him to leave

00:07:57.630 --> 00:07:58.430
because

00:07:59.070 --> 00:08:00.750
he's become special to you

00:08:01.190 --> 00:08:02.830
and you can't bear to part with him.

00:08:02.830 --> 00:08:03.480
Is that so?

00:08:11.600 --> 00:08:12.830
Love.

00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:14.680
What is love?

00:08:16.830 --> 00:08:18.480
Love is

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:20.160
when her nearness

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.490
drives your heartbeat into frenzy.

00:08:21.490 --> 00:08:22.480
♪ While the rain fades ♪

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:23.920
Your pulse races,

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:24.870
♪ I wander once more
through the old city upstream ♪

00:08:24.870 --> 00:08:26.750
but you pretend to be calm.

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:30.200
♪ Yet I cannot erase ♪

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:31.260
Step back a little.

00:08:31.320 --> 00:08:31.510
♪ Mist-veiled tales
that stir the river tides ♪

00:08:31.510 --> 00:08:32.960
Your perfume is too strong.

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.220
It gives me a headache.

00:08:36.990 --> 00:08:37.320
♪ In fading dreams ♪

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:39.580
Could it be that young lady Lu Yingying
of the Lu family

00:08:39.580 --> 00:08:41.270
♪ Lanterns stain
the worldly bustle with their glow ♪

00:08:41.270 --> 00:08:43.669
has captured our Chief Commander's heart?

00:08:44.410 --> 00:08:45.960
♪ Today's tales sound off-key and hollow ♪

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:46.600
Do you

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:48.000
like him?

00:08:48.630 --> 00:08:50.000
Is it that difficult to answer?

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:52.200
♪ Distorted, or left in fragments ♪

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:52.960
I...

00:08:53.490 --> 00:08:55.000
♪ I heard the legends rise like the wind ♪

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:55.630
Forget it.

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:57.750
♪ Only to fall back into nothingness ♪

00:08:57.750 --> 00:08:58.200
Hui.

00:08:58.630 --> 00:08:59.820
♪ I dare not disturb
the toll of the bell ♪

00:08:59.870 --> 00:09:00.350
Hui.

00:09:00.350 --> 00:09:02.020
♪ Nor dare I awaken the dream ♪

00:09:02.510 --> 00:09:04.130
♪ Fearing the retelling ♪

00:09:04.750 --> 00:09:06.910
♪ Could never capture
that breathtaking glance back then ♪

00:09:06.910 --> 00:09:08.170
Chief Commander,
you really like Lu Yingying?

00:09:08.170 --> 00:09:09.580
♪ Loving you was devotion
beneath moon and breeze ♪

00:09:10.020 --> 00:09:11.210
♪ Both ordinary love and hate ♪

00:09:11.430 --> 00:09:12.150
♪ Thus the era was shaken ♪

00:09:12.150 --> 00:09:13.440
Fine, I won't ask anymore.

00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:13.710
I just want to know

00:09:13.710 --> 00:09:14.630
♪ In youthful years of innocence ♪

00:09:14.630 --> 00:09:15.310
who made our Chief Commander unhappy.

00:09:15.310 --> 00:09:18.150
♪ When meetings would not come again ♪

00:09:18.850 --> 00:09:23.930
♪ The mortal realm was bound
to start yet never end ♪

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:29.480
Chief Commander.

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:31.000
Looking at you like this,

00:09:31.150 --> 00:09:33.510
don't tell me you're in love with someone.

00:09:33.670 --> 00:09:34.870
What is love?

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:37.000
Love is

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:38.720
when her nearness

00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:40.960
drives your heartbeat into frenzy.

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.480
Your pulse races,

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:45.320
but you pretend to be calm.

00:09:56.000 --> 00:09:56.650
Why are you looking at me like that?

00:09:56.650 --> 00:09:58.140
♪ When the rain subsides ♪

00:09:58.720 --> 00:09:58.890
Nothing.

00:09:58.890 --> 00:10:00.030
♪ The moon above the turret
shines from afar ♪

00:10:00.030 --> 00:10:01.560
My Lady, you're beautiful.

00:10:04.050 --> 00:10:05.510
♪ The world would say ♪

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:09.260
♪ Romance cannot bear
the clamor of splendor ♪

00:10:11.870 --> 00:10:13.630
♪ Her graceful shadow sways ♪

00:10:14.490 --> 00:10:17.270
♪ New favors and old grudges
hard to dispel ♪

00:10:19.480 --> 00:10:23.970
♪ How many things are now left behind? ♪

00:10:24.550 --> 00:10:28.020
♪ Turning through time into a ballad ♪

00:10:28.880 --> 00:10:31.070
♪ I heard the legends rise like the wind ♪

00:10:31.520 --> 00:10:33.070
♪ Only to fall back into nothingness ♪

00:10:33.850 --> 00:10:34.920
♪ I dare not disturb
the toll of the bell ♪

00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:36.990
♪ Nor dare I awaken the dream ♪

00:10:37.800 --> 00:10:39.330
♪ Fearing the retelling ♪

00:10:39.790 --> 00:10:40.440
♪ Hastily blaming the cruelty of time ♪

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:41.910
How can I be certain

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:43.580
whether I'm in love?

00:10:43.580 --> 00:10:44.600
♪ Yet it still knocks
on my heart and soul ♪

00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:45.390
Get close to the person you might love

00:10:45.390 --> 00:10:46.440
♪ Like a dream from another life ♪

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:46.910
and you'll know.

00:10:46.910 --> 00:10:48.170
♪ Reincarnating in words ♪

00:10:49.090 --> 00:10:50.290
♪ Afraid others won't understand ♪

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:53.290
♪ Afraid of stirring emotions
for no reason ♪

00:10:54.190 --> 00:10:59.570
♪ Better to have a beginning with no end ♪